<p>If this has run successfully, you will now see a new folder in your repository called â€˜_siteâ€™. Upload the contents of this folder into your S3 bucket by drag and drop or through the â€˜Uploadâ€™ function on AWS.</p>

<p>At this point, your site is live. Head into the properties tab, scroll to the bottom and click on the link shown in the â€˜Static Website Hostingâ€™ box. If everything has gone well, you should now see your site.</p>

